scene.message:
Brown: Fuga~??{nl}
Someone came out of me{nl}
and said hello.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That?{nl}
We've decided to call{nl}
it a Persona.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: At least for now,{nl}
it doesn't seem to be{nl}
an enemy.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What do you mean?{nl}
Don't tell me {ctl0f:1} and{nl}
Mayuzumi are that too?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Whether they're "that"{nl}
or not, I don't know, but{nl}
we do share one thing.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yeah, ever since that{nl}
weird dream, we can call{nl}
those - Personas, was it?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Somehow, only those who{nl}
saw that butterfly in their{nl}
dream have gained the power.{waitkey}{clearbox}It seems connected to this{nl}
demon uproar as well.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ugh! Toro used a{nl}
Persona too. Did he have{nl}
the butterfly dream as well?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}...{wait_fr:18}I don't think so.{nl}
Like a Knife, what matters{nl}
is how you use it.{waitkey}{clearbox}With its use, it can help{nl}
people or harm them.{waitkey}In short, it's the character{nl}
of the one who wields it.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I think not.{nl}
Even the same power is used{nl}
differently by each person.{waitkey}{clearbox}Dynamite has the power to{nl}
kill, but it can also{nl}
open a tunnel.{waitkey}{clearbox}In the end it's the wielder's{nl}
character. Use power for{nl}
greed, and you reap what{waitkey}you sow.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Character, huh~{nl}
No problem there.{waitkey}I see!!{waitkey}{clearbox}The butterfly must think this:{nl}
make Lord Brown a champion{nl}
of justice to save the town{waitkey}and school, or something.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you all bow your heads{nl}
and beg me, well,{nl}
I suppose I've no choice.{waitkey}{clearbox}I, the great me, shall{nl}
lend you my power!{nl}
Everyone, follow me!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Well, if he wants{nl}
to come along, let him{nl}
do as he likes.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Oh-ho?{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly, come on~♥{nl}
You want me to come along~♥{nl}
Let's all be more honest, eh?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey hey hey{waitkey}{clearbox}Yukino herself said "by all{nl}
means"! There's no way{nl}
I can refuse!{waitkey}{clearbox}Besides, from what I hear,{nl}
the school ended up like{nl}
this 'cause of you, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}Put me up as leader and{nl}
you can't go wrong.{waitkey}{clearbox}Just trust me and{nl}
follow along!!{nl}
Dehyahyahyahyahya!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Where are you looking,{nl}
flashing a peace sign?{waitkey}{clearbox}C'mon, quit dawdling!{nl}
Let's go!!{waitkey}{ret}
